news/twin-peaks-into-the-night-reimagines-the-classic-show-as-a-ps1-game-3481745">《双峰：入夜》将经典节目重新演绎为 PS1 游戏，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
