/tags/xbox-series-s">Xbox Series S</a>版本提供八人本地分屏多人游戏。新扩展名为“Call Of The Machine”，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/machinegames">MachineGames</a>制作，有 28 个关卡和一张多人死亡竞赛地图。</p><p> 1998 年发布的原版游戏的两个任务包“清算”和“归零地”也与重制版捆绑在一起。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/midway">Midway</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/nintendo-64">任天堂 64</a>版<em>《雷神之锤 2》</em>也出现在游戏中，也许最相关的是，《Sonic Mayhem》的原始配乐也被保留了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3481735" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3481735" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3481735" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/quake-2-remaster-is-out-now-for-all-platforms-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3481735" class="wp-caption-text"> 《雷神之锤 2》图片来源：Bethesda Softworks</figcaption></figure><p>在原版游戏重制版发布后，id Software 于 2021 年开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/id-software-is-hiring-for-the-development-of-a-long-running-action-fps-title-3083405">为传闻中的<em>《雷神之锤 2》</em>重制版进行招募</a>。此外，韩国游戏评级和管理委员会于今年 6 月对<em>《雷神之锤 2》</em>进行了评级。 Given that the board did the same thing by <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-remastered-version-of-quake-is-available-now-3025208">rating the Quake re